    <title>StableDiffusion初尝试和探索</title>
    <link href="https://vymv.github.io/StableDiffusion%E5%88%9D%E5%B0%9D%E8%AF%95%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%A2%E7%B4%A2/"/>
    <id>https://vymv.github.io/StableDiffusion%E5%88%9D%E5%B0%9D%E8%AF%95%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%A2%E7%B4%A2/</id>
    <published>2023-05-14T15:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-05-15T02:24:23.783Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="模型"><a href="#模型" class="headerlink" title="模型"></a>模型</h3><p>分为基础模型和微调模型（lora等）。</p><h4 id="基础模型"><a href="#基础模型" class="headerlink" title="基础模型"></a>基础模型</h4><ul><li>基础模型通常非常大，以著名动漫模型anything为例，fp32的精度模型大小为4.27G，fp16的精度大小为2.13G（精度越高出图质量越好）。</li><li>有的基础模型擅长二次元创作，有的基础模型擅长真实感创作，可以根据需要切换。</li></ul><h4 id="Lora"><a href="#Lora" class="headerlink" title="Lora"></a>Lora</h4><p>Lora是一种对大模型的微调模型，需要配合大模型一起使用，通常只有几百M。</p><p>比如，GPT-3有1750亿参数，为了让它能干特定领域的活儿，需要做微调，但是如果直接对GPT-3做微调，成本太高太麻烦了。 </p><p>Lora的做法是，冻结预训练好的模型权重参数，然后在每个Transformer块里注入可训练的层，由于不需要对模型的权重参数重新计算梯度，所以，大大减少了需要训练的计算量。 </p><p>研究发现，Lora的微调质量与全模型微调相当。</p><p>Lora通常由几百张或几千张特定风格的图片训练而成，你也可以训练自己的Lora。</p><h4 id="Vae"><a href="#Vae" class="headerlink" title="Vae"></a>Vae</h4><p>可以视为模型的滤镜，如果生成的图片灰暗，饱和度很低，很可能是没有设置Vae，如这张图：</p><img src="/StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/image-20230505235253322.png" style="zoom:50%;" /><h3 id="模型下载使用"><a href="#模型下载使用" class="headerlink" title="模型下载使用"></a>模型下载使用</h3><h4 id="模型网站"><a href="#模型网站" class="headerlink" title="模型网站"></a>模型网站</h4><ul><li><p><a href="https://civitai.com/%EF%BC%88%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E9%AD%94%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90%EF%BC%89">https://civitai.com/（需要魔法，推荐）</a></p></li><li><p><a href="https://huggingface.co/%EF%BC%88%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89AI%E7%BB%98%E7%94%BB%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%EF%BC%89">https://huggingface.co/（综合模型网站，不只有AI绘画模型的网站）</a></p></li></ul><h4 id="一些喜欢的模型和lora"><a href="#一些喜欢的模型和lora" class="headerlink" title="一些喜欢的模型和lora"></a>一些喜欢的模型和lora</h4><ul><li><p>AnythingElse V4（<a href="https://civitai.com/models/4855/anythingelse-v4%EF%BC%89%E7%94%A8%E6%9D%A5%E7%94%BB%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1%E5%85%83%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%AA%E4%BC%9A%E7%94%BB%E6%89%8B%E3%80%82">https://civitai.com/models/4855/anythingelse-v4）用来画二次元人物，不太会画手。</a></p></li><li><p>Counterfeit-V3.0（<a href="https://civitai.com/models/4468/counterfeit-v30%EF%BC%89%E5%96%9C%E6%AC%A2%E7%94%A8%E6%9D%A5%E7%94%BB%E9%A3%8E%E6%99%AF%EF%BC%8C%E6%90%AD%E9%85%8D%E4%B8%8B%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84Lora%E3%80%82">https://civitai.com/models/4468/counterfeit-v30）喜欢用来画风景，搭配下面的Lora。</a></p><ul><li>Ghibli_Style_Concept_scenery_V3（<a href="https://civitai.com/models/28511/ghiblistyleconceptsceneryv3%EF%BC%89">https://civitai.com/models/28511/ghiblistyleconceptsceneryv3）</a></li></ul></li><li><p>TMND-Mix（<a href="https://civitai.com/models/27259/tmnd-mix%EF%BC%89%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1%E5%85%83%E9%A3%8E%E6%99%AF%E5%92%8C%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9%E9%83%BD%E5%BE%88%E6%93%85%E9%95%BF%E3%80%82">https://civitai.com/models/27259/tmnd-mix）二次元风景和人物都很擅长。</a></p></li><li><p>Standing Full Body with Background Style LoRA（<a href="https://civitai.com/models/16997?modelVersionId=20072%EF%BC%89%E8%AE%A9%E4%BA%8C%E6%AC%A1%E5%85%83%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2%E7%AB%8B%E7%BB%98%E6%8B%A5%E6%9C%89%E5%B0%8F%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E3%80%82">https://civitai.com/models/16997?modelVersionId=20072）让二次元角色立绘拥有小背景。</a></p></li></ul><h4 id="基础模型下载使用"><a href="#基础模型下载使用" class="headerlink" title="基础模型下载使用"></a>基础模型下载使用</h4><p>以Anything为例：<a href="https://huggingface.co/andite/anything-v4.0/tree/main">https://huggingface.co/andite/anything-v4.0/tree/main</a></p><p>在hugging face打开可以看到很多选择，有.ckpt后缀的，也有.safetensor后缀。</p><p>safetensor比ckpt更安全，加载时间更快。更具体的区别详见：<a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/611248399">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/611248399</a></p><p><img src="/StableDiffusion%E5%88%9D%E5%B0%9D%E8%AF%95%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%A2%E7%B4%A2/image-20230505231557638.png" alt="image-20230505231557638"></p><p>C站右侧的信息中可以看到基础模型的type是checkpoint。</p><p>Hash代表了该模型的id，如果是AI生成的raw图片，我们都能读取其prompt及参数信息以及模型hash，不同版本的同种模型hash也会不同。</p><p><a href="https://civitai.com/models/4855/anythingelse-v4">https://civitai.com/models/4855/anythingelse-v4</a></p><p><img src="/StableDiffusion%E5%88%9D%E5%B0%9D%E8%AF%95%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%A2%E7%B4%A2/image-20230505232337468.png" alt="image-20230505232337468"></p><p>C站下面有很多用户使用该模型生成的一些出色作品，并提供了prompt参考。</p><p>下载好模型后放置在stable-diffusion-webui&#x2F;models\Stable-diffusion下。</p><p>点集右侧刷新，即可选择自己的模型。</p><p><img src="/StableDiffusion%E5%88%9D%E5%B0%9D%E8%AF%95%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%A2%E7%B4%A2/image-20230505233243426.png" alt="image-20230505233243426"></p><p>切换大模型由于参数量巨大，通常需要等待几分钟的时间。</p><p>一些大模型会提供官方的negative prompt，需要一并下载，例如：<a href="https://civitai.com/models/4468/counterfeit-v30%EF%BC%8C%E6%94%BE%E7%BD%AE%E5%9C%A8/stable-diffusion-webui/embeddings%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E4%B8%8B%E3%80%82">https://civitai.com/models/4468/counterfeit-v30，放置在\stable-diffusion-webui\embeddings目录下。</a></p><h4 id="lora下载使用"><a href="#lora下载使用" class="headerlink" title="lora下载使用"></a>lora下载使用</h4><p>以Standing Full Body with Background Style LoRA为例</p><p><a href="https://civitai.com/models/16997/standing-full-body-with-background-style-lora">https://civitai.com/models/16997/standing-full-body-with-background-style-lora</a></p><p>下载后放置在stable-diffusion-webui\models\Lora下</p><p>在右侧生成下面的第三个按钮可以选择lora（没有记得刷新）</p><p><img src="/StableDiffusion%E5%88%9D%E5%B0%9D%E8%AF%95%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%A2%E7%B4%A2/image-20230505233615584.png" alt="image-20230505233615584"></p><p>选择后，会被自动加入到prompt中，冒号后面可以调节lora权重，可以调用多个不同的lora并调节比例。</p><h4 id="vae下载使用"><a href="#vae下载使用" class="headerlink" title="vae下载使用"></a>vae下载使用</h4><p>模型通常会有配套的vae</p><p>根据这个帖子<a href="https://huggingface.co/andite/anything-v4.0/discussions/65">https://huggingface.co/andite/anything-v4.0/discussions/65</a></p><p>我选择了kl-f8-anime2.ckpt（<a href="https://huggingface.co/hakurei/waifu-diffusion-v1-4/blob/main/vae/kl-f8-anime2.ckpt%EF%BC%89">https://huggingface.co/hakurei/waifu-diffusion-v1-4/blob/main/vae/kl-f8-anime2.ckpt）</a></p><p>下好之后放置在stable-diffusion-webui\models\VAE下</p><p>在界面这里设置VAE</p><p><img src="/StableDiffusion%E5%88%9D%E5%B0%9D%E8%AF%95%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%A2%E7%B4%A2/image-20230505234709733.png" alt="image-20230505234709733"></p><h4 id="作品生成"><a href="#作品生成" class="headerlink" title="作品生成"></a>作品生成</h4><ul><li><p>通常先生成低分辨率图像</p></li><li><p>再通过放大，微调和修复细节</p></li><li><p>设置好模型prompt及各种参数后，点击生成，就能在webui界面看到结果，output目录下也会保存每一张生成的图片</p></li></ul><h3 id="功能及参数"><a href="#功能及参数" class="headerlink" title="功能及参数"></a>功能及参数</h3><h4 id="文生图"><a href="#文生图" class="headerlink" title="文生图"></a>文生图</h4><p>prompt的权重和prompt的顺序有关，写在前面的prompt权重更高。</p><p>（发现模型生成的是黄头发，想让它画黑头发，但在prompt末尾加了black hair，模型却还是不听我的。。。后来知道是权重太低了）</p><p>使用括号：(prompt)，能将该词的权重乘1.1，如果双层括号，则乘两次1.1以此类推，相反的中括号[]能将权重降低1.1倍。也可以直接指定权重（black:1.4），可根据出图反馈动态调整各词汇的权重。</p><p>通常prompt以这样的格式书写：</p><p>第一段：画质 tag，画风 tag</p><p>第二段：画面主体，主体强调，主体细节概括（主体可以是人、事、物、景）画面核心内容</p><p>第三段：画面场景细节，或人物细节，embedding tag（Lora）。</p><p><strong>常用的词汇：</strong></p><p><strong>风景图 prompt</strong></p><p>Landsape, (masterpiece, best quality:1.2), ultra detailed, cinematic lighting, beautiful lighting,lensflare,raytracing,HDR</p><p><strong>二次元 girl prompt</strong></p><p>1girl,solo,masterpiece, best quality, looking_at_viewer,panorama,Beautiful Lighting,cinematiclighting,ray tracing,lensflare,tachi-e,full body, </p><p><strong>negative prompt</strong></p><p>nsfw,(EasyNegative),(worst quality, low quality:1.4), (bad anatomy), (inaccurate limb:1.2),poorly eyes, extra digit,fewer digits,six fingers,(extra arms,extra legs:1.2),text,cropped,jpegartifacts,(signature), (watermark), username,blurry,more than five fingers in one palm,no thumb,no nails, title, multiple view, Reference sheet, curvy, plump, fat, muscular female, strabismus,</p><p><strong>一些参数</strong></p><p>采样方法：一般都选择DPM++ 2M Karras</p><p>迭代步数（Steps）：顾名思义，迭代次数越高，生成的图细节越好，需要的时间也越长。</p><p>提示词相关性（CFG）：一般在图生图中使用，文生图默认即可。</p><p>随机种子：-1代表随机选择一个种子，也可以填写指定的种子，AI出图的随机性来源于此。</p><h4 id="图生图"><a href="#图生图" class="headerlink" title="图生图"></a>图生图</h4><p><strong>一些参数</strong></p><p>提示词相关性（CFG）：顾名思义</p><p>重绘幅度（Denoising）：不清楚为什么“降噪”代表重绘幅度，通常如果是放大修复细节，重绘幅度设置为0.1~0.2，如果普通图生图则0.5~0.9都有。</p><p>如下图，左侧为原图，中间重绘幅度为，还能清楚地看到画卷展开，右侧重绘幅度为，已经看不到画卷了。</p><center class = "half">    <img src = "/StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/279.png" width = "300">    <img src = "/StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00010-53652654.png" width = "200">    <img src = "/StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00002-604226150.png" width = "200"></center><table><thead><tr><th><img src="/StableDiffusion%E5%88%9D%E5%B0%9D%E8%AF%95%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%A2%E7%B4%A2/279.png" alt="279.png"></th><th><img src="/StableDiffusion%E5%88%9D%E5%B0%9D%E8%AF%95%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%A2%E7%B4%A2/00010-53652654.png" alt="00010-53652654.png"></th><th><img src="/StableDiffusion%E5%88%9D%E5%B0%9D%E8%AF%95%E5%92%8C%E6%8E%A2%E7%B4%A2/00002-604226150.png" alt="00002-604226150.png"></th></tr></thead></table><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br><span class="line">89</span><br><span class="line">90</span><br><span class="line">91</span><br><span class="line">92</span><br><span class="line">93</span><br><span class="line">94</span><br><span class="line">95</span><br><span class="line">96</span><br><span class="line">97</span><br><span class="line">98</span><br><span class="line">99</span><br><span class="line">100</span><br><span class="line">101</span><br><span class="line">102</span><br><span class="line">103</span><br><span class="line">104</span><br><span class="line">105</span><br><span class="line">106</span><br><span class="line">107</span><br><span class="line">108</span><br><span class="line">109</span><br><span class="line">110</span><br><span class="line">111</span><br><span class="line">112</span><br><span class="line">113</span><br><span class="line">114</span><br><span class="line">115</span><br><span class="line">116</span><br><span class="line">117</span><br><span class="line">118</span><br><span class="line">119</span><br><span class="line">120</span><br><span class="line">121</span><br><span class="line">122</span><br><span class="line">123</span><br><span class="line">124</span><br><span class="line">125</span><br><span class="line">126</span><br><span class="line">127</span><br><span class="line">128</span><br><span class="line">129</span><br><span class="line">130</span><br><span class="line">131</span><br><span class="line">132</span><br><span class="line">133</span><br><span class="line">134</span><br><span class="line">135</span><br><span class="line">136</span><br><span class="line">137</span><br><span class="line">138</span><br><span class="line">139</span><br><span class="line">140</span><br><span class="line">141</span><br><span class="line">142</span><br><span class="line">143</span><br><span class="line">144</span><br><span class="line">145</span><br><span class="line">146</span><br><span class="line">147</span><br><span class="line">148</span><br><span class="line">149</span><br><span class="line">150</span><br><span class="line">151</span><br><span class="line">152</span><br><span class="line">153</span><br><span class="line">154</span><br><span class="line">155</span><br><span class="line">156</span><br><span class="line">157</span><br><span class="line">158</span><br><span class="line">159</span><br><span class="line">160</span><br><span class="line">161</span><br><span class="line">162</span><br><span class="line">163</span><br><span class="line">164</span><br><span class="line">165</span><br><span class="line">166</span><br><span class="line">167</span><br><span class="line">168</span><br><span class="line">169</span><br><span class="line">170</span><br><span class="line">171</span><br><span class="line">172</span><br><span class="line">173</span><br><span class="line">174</span><br><span class="line">175</span><br><span class="line">176</span><br><span class="line">177</span><br><span class="line">178</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#### 放大</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">可以是纯放大。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">也可以用来修复细节，给予一定的重绘幅度，画面有时会出现一些较为明显的向好改变。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">例如下面这张，除了手部，其他部分都不错。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;img src=&quot;/StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00058-452352455.png&quot; alt=&quot;00058-452352455&quot;  /&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">放大后：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;img src=&quot;/StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00004-1929881450.png&quot; alt=&quot;00004-1929881450&quot; style=&quot;zoom:50%;&quot; /&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">因为negative prompt中给bad finger加了很高的权重，模型倾向于不画右手了。。。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">后来调了种子又出了一张还不错的：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;img src=&quot;/StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/1.png&quot; alt=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;zoom: 33%;&quot; /&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#### 反推prompt</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- 试了试CLIP反推，感觉很多细节没有描写到位。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![326](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/326.webp)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">SD给出的prompt是：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">a woman dressed in a white and gold outfit with a cat on her lap and a clock on her arm, Fan Qi, official art, a character portrait, ukiyo-e</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">但显然不是cat而是fox，手摇铃被描述为clock，可能是训练的时候没见过吧</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">用上面的prompt再生成一张图试试：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;imgStableDiffusion初尝试和探索/QQ图片20230515000205.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;QQ图片20230515000205&quot; style=&quot;zoom:50%;&quot; /&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![326](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/QQ图片20230515000205.jpg)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#### 图片信息</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">顾名思义，能读到AI作图的prompt和参数。可以用来学习网络上各种优秀作品的prompt。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![image-20230506000831230](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/image-20230506000831230.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#### 种子微调</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;img src=&quot;StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/QQ图片20230515000503.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;QQ图片20230515000503&quot; style=&quot;zoom:50%;&quot; /&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">生成了一张不错的图，想多生成一些类似的，挑一张更好的</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- 在随机种子这里打钩</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![image-20230515000707407](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/image-20230515000707407.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​随机种子和差异随机种子都填写这张图片的Seed</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- 调整差异强度，例如0.18</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- 调整每批数量，例如4，点击生成</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![img](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/$VH@RU86XBX_G9`ZQZ1HQ5R.jpg)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#### 修复手指</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">画不好手指是AI模型的通病了，通常有以下几种解决方法：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- inpaint（局部重绘）</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  通过在异样手指处手绘蒙版，修复手指</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;center class = &quot;half&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;img src = &quot;/StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00000-3058949938.png&quot; width = &quot;300&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;img src = &quot;/StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00007-3058949938.png&quot; width = &quot;300&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/center&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- 放大</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  （见上文）</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- control net（TODO）</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">- Lora（TODO）</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#### 一些生僻参数</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">经常在C站的图片信息里看到的生僻参数解释。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">**ENSD**</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">默认建议值31337</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">https://www.reddit.com/r/StableDiffusion/comments/10d093y/ensd_what_is_it/</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">**Clip skip：**</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">默认2</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/621276242</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">### 一些自己生成的好看的图</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;img src=&quot;/StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00175-654345.png&quot; alt=&quot;00175-654345&quot; style=&quot;zoom:100%;&quot; /&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![00003-24352435](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00003-24352435.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![00062-365645534](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00062-365645534.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![00102-2768684264](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00102-2768684264.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![00051-653425](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00051-653425.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![00241-470777179](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00241-470777179.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![00168-3250371279](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00168-3250371279.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![00325-3193787633](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00325-3193787633-1683470099936.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![00020-264466535](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00020-264466535.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![00313-2789391629](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00313-2789391629.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![00363-654364532543](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00363-654364532543.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![00233-4038965757](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00233-4038965757.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![00305-2867403363](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00305-2867403363.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![00323-3207705890](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00323-3207705890.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![00018-6546345](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00018-6546345.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![00296-1539898891](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00296-1539898891.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![00252-2482152167](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00252-2482152167.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![00333-541990144](StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00333-541990144.png)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![00002-43589576](/StableDiffusion初尝试和探索/00002-43589576.png)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
